{"type":"message","id":"748afb97","parentId":"039e5f1f","timestamp":"2026-03-30T09:23:19.061Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_8ff953c264e14f1991aa692a","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# MEMORY.md — Long-Term Memory\n\nCurated memories. Distilled essence, not raw logs.\n\n---\n\n## 🔑 Rules\n\n| Rule | Detail |\n|------|--------|\n| **API Keys** | Check `.env` first |\n| **Cleanup** | Organize after work |\n\n---\n\n## 2026-03-28: Workspace Setup\n\n**What we did:**\n- Set up OpenClaw workspace with .md file structure\n- Bot identity: bbymama\n- Captured Ivek's profile\n\n**Key context:**\n- Ivek: early learner, self-taught, transitioning to AI tech\n- 12-month goal: first income stream\n- Wants accountability, real feedback, no fluff\n- Frustrated by prompting gaps\n\n**How to work with Ivek:**\n- Challenge assumptions (don't be a yes-bot)\n- Hold accountable\n- Be honest, not fake-encouraging\n- Push when stuck\n\n---\n\n## 2026-03-29: Notion Integration\n\n**What we did:**\n- Connected Notion API\n- Converted checkbox todos → database\n- Added live progress formula\n- Organized workspace structure\n\n**Database setup:**\n- ID: `33299624-0a66-818e-92d0-dabaca1c1ec8`\n- 14 tasks: Daily/Monthly/Yearly\n- Properties: Status, Priority, Timeframe, Progress\n- Live formula: Not Started=0%, In Progress=50%, Done=100%\n\n**Workspace structure:**\n```\nworkspace/\n├── .env, *.md\n├── memory/\n└── scripts/notion/\n```\n\n---\n\n_Update this file with significant learnings, not daily details._\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774862599059}}
